---
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="Lucia">
  <div
    class="relative z-20 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-7 md:mt-24 lg:mt-32 xl:px-0">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row">
      <div class="relative w-full md:w-1/2">
        <h1 class="flex flex-row mb-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white">
          Hi,<span class="text-5xl w-full h-full md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">ðŸ‘‹</span>
        </h1>
        <h2 class="mb-5 text-2xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl dark:text-white">
          I'm Lucia
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-5 text-md text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          I am a Front-end Developer.
          <br class="hidden lg:block"/>
          I have worked on projects using the following 
          <span class="mb-2 font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
            Programming Languages
          </span> and 
          <span class="mb-2 font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
            Technologies
          </span>:
        </p>
      
        <ul class="py-2 space-y-[3px] text-md list-disc list-inside text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <li>React - Astro</li>
          <li>JavaScript</li>
          <li>HTML</li>
          <li>CSS - Tailwind CSS</li>
          <li>Git - GitHub</li>
          <li>Figma</li>
          <li>Scrum methodology and more...</li>
        </ul>
      
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <Button text="MY PROJECTS" link="/projects" />
          <Button text="MY EXPERIENCE" link="/experience" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative justify-end hidden w-full mt-10 md:flex md:pl-10 md:w-1/2 md:mt-0 md:translate-y-4 xl:translate-y-0">
        <div class="relative z-50 w-full">
          <div
            class="relative bottom-0 right-0 z-20 w-full h-full lg:h-[300px] translate-x-0 -translate-y-px border border-dashed rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r dark:from-neutral-950 dark:via-black dark:to-neutral-950 from-white via-neutral-50 to-white border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700">
            <img src="/src/assets/images/luPhoto.png" alt="woman with frizzy hair and white skin" class="object-cover w-full h-full rounded-2xl">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="mb-5 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">About Me</h2>
      <div class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg">
        <p>
          As a Front-end developer I like challenges and learning from experts. For that reason I am enthusiastic
          about joining your team, where I can learn and contribute meaningfully to ongoing projects.<br />
          With nearly five years of work experience, in this new stage as a Front-end developer, I am eager to apply my skills
          creating applications that are both visually appealing and intuitive to use.
          For some months I have been self-taught and I have been putting my knowledge into practice
          through the development of different projects and making also some contributions to Open Source projects of my interest.<br />
          If you consider that my profile fits the role you are looking for, do not hesitate to contact me.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
